    "title": "Looking for Real Estate Agent at Mahagun Group",
    "description": "Mahagun Group has an exciting opening for a Real Estate Agent at our Ranchi office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Mahagun Group:\nMahagun Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mahagun Group!",
